# Infrastructure & Deployment

## VPS: box.makkib.com
- IP: 135.125.179.131
- OS: Ubuntu 24
- Hosting: Hetzner CPX22 (4 vCPU, 8 GB RAM)
- Domains: INWX
- Firewall: iptables — NEVER use ufw
- Reverse proxy: nginx with `include /etc/nginx/mcp.d/*.conf`

## Monorepo on VPS
The repo is cloned to TWO locations (different system users):
- `/home/cdapi/mcp-stack` — runs CenterDevice MCP (user: `cdapi`)
- `/home/bdroapi/mcp-stack` — runs Bidrento MCP (user: `bdroapi`)

